thread.title: Nirvan

author: Nirvan
title: Nirvan
text:
Bought a pair of Sidi wire Carbon shoes recently, obviously we not talking about the quality of the product as every body knows how good these shoes are.
Quite happy with the price that PBK had compared with elsewhere and the shoes arrived in two weeks, longer than other famous online retails (apparently should not name the competitors in the reviews so lets leave it at that) so I give it a 4 stars.
